    "recommended_first_use": "Attach this pack to AI platform intake, MCP server approval, retrieval-augmented-agent design review, and quarterly context-source recertification.",
    "sales_motion": "Lead with open context provenance, then sell hosted context signing, customer evidence ingestion, retrieval policy enforcement, source drift alerts, and trust-center exports."
